#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/messaging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following metrics can be gathered per channel, identified with the `channel` tag:"
msgstr "可以按每个渠道收集以下指标，这些指标通过 `渠道` 标签进行标识："

